## .NET build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
artifacts/
# Editor's Roslyn BuildHost writes literal-backslash dirs (bin\Debug) on macOS,
# which [Bb]in/ does NOT match. ? matches the backslash. These corrupt MSBuild
# globbing (MSB3552), so they must never be tracked.
bin?Debug/
obj?Debug/
bin?Release/
obj?Release/

